Package com.github.tnakamot.json.parser

This package provides classes to parse JSON text based on RFC 8259.

JSONLexer splits a given JSONText into a sequence of tokens. JSONParser semantically analyzes the sequence of tokens and generate JSONValue.

See Also:
RFC 8259
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JSONLexer
    An implementation of lexical analyzer for JSON texts.
    JSONParser
    An implementation of a parser of JSON texts.
    JSONParserErrorMessageFormat
    A data structure to hold the switches to change the error message format of JSONParserException.
    JSONParserErrorMessageFormat.Builder
    Builder class of JSONParserErrorMessageFormat.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    JSONParserException
    Thrown when a JSON lexical analyzer fails to tokenize a given JSON text due to a syntax error.
